{
  "texts": [
    "The advantage of XpertAI is that it overcomes these vulnerabilities by using the RAG approach.",
    "We further evaluated the precision of the generated hypotheses by XpertAI and compared with GPT-4o explanations.",
    "For each task and each feature that is identified in the XpertAI explanation, we extracted each proposed hypothesis and labeled the correlation of the feature with the property under study (OMS, PLD etc.)",
    "as positive, negative, or unclear.",
    "An example of an unclear correlation is \"Metal ions with favorable redox properties might be more likely to form stable open metal sites.\""
  ]
}